    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Whistles or other simple instruments used to imitate the sound of a particular animal, such as a bird or a deer; often designed for hunters or bird watchers to attract animals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
